# Beginner Python Practice

This folder contains beginner-friendly Python practice problems that I solved while strengthening my programming fundamentals.

The goal of these exercises is to build a solid understanding of core Python concepts through consistent practice and problem-solving.
## Purpose

These problems focus on developing:

- Problem-solving skills
- Logical thinking
- Code readability
- Confidence with Python syntax
- Understanding of programming fundamentals

## Difficulty Level

**Beginner / Easy**

The problems in this folder are suitable for:

- New Python learners
- Students
- Career switchers entering technology
- Anyone looking to strengthen programming basics



## Note

This folder is part of my Python learning and portfolio journey. As I continue learning, I will keep adding new problems and improving existing solutions.
